1
00:01:28,940 --> 00:01:35,570
Winter Begonia

2
00:01:35,570 --> 00:01:37,979
Episode 9

3
00:01:41,740 --> 00:01:43,090
You took me here

4
00:01:43,100 --> 00:01:44,050
but hide it from me.

5
00:01:46,100 --> 00:01:47,450
Gosh!

6
00:02:03,500 --> 00:02:04,370
Good.

7
00:02:05,900 --> 00:02:07,090
In some days,

8
00:02:07,420 --> 00:02:10,210
the painter will be a master.

9
00:02:13,140 --> 00:02:14,770
Can you do me a favor?

10
00:02:17,579 --> 00:02:20,290
I can repair the cave.

11
00:02:21,820 --> 00:02:23,650
What I need to do is making it firm.

12
00:02:24,820 --> 00:02:27,970
It can be maintained for 60 years.

13
00:02:28,820 --> 00:02:29,690
Is it enough?

14
00:02:33,060 --> 00:02:34,450
60 years?

15
00:02:36,900 --> 00:02:38,410
That’s enough.

16
00:02:40,260 --> 00:02:41,410
But,

17
00:02:42,540 --> 00:02:44,410
it’s unfair to me

18
00:02:45,380 --> 00:02:47,850
if everyone can go through the cave

19
00:02:48,579 --> 00:02:50,490
after it’s repaired.

20
00:02:51,780 --> 00:02:54,250
What else do you want?

21
00:02:56,300 --> 00:02:57,170
I want

22
00:02:58,420 --> 00:03:00,970
a lock in the cave.

23
00:03:01,940 --> 00:03:03,090
When

24
00:03:03,620 --> 00:03:04,690
I want it to collapse,

25
00:03:05,260 --> 00:03:06,610
it will collapse.

26
00:03:07,220 --> 00:03:10,330
You’d rather ruin your house
than let others live in it?

27
00:03:13,300 --> 00:03:15,370
You look like a socialite,

28
00:03:15,940 --> 00:03:18,970
but you are not generous like them.

29
00:03:19,980 --> 00:03:23,130
This is an arduous work.

30
00:03:24,860 --> 00:03:26,810
You ask me to do it

31
00:03:27,060 --> 00:03:28,650
because you trust me.

32
00:03:29,100 --> 00:03:30,329
So,

33
00:03:32,340 --> 00:03:35,290
I’ll ask something more for the payment.

34
00:03:44,579 --> 00:03:46,290
Write a number that you want.

35
00:03:47,940 --> 00:03:49,329
Mr. Cheng, don’t misunderstand.

36
00:03:49,620 --> 00:03:51,170
This is not what I want.

37
00:03:52,180 --> 00:03:53,130
I heard

38
00:03:53,820 --> 00:03:56,010
that you are the brother-in-law of Commander Cao.

39
00:03:57,900 --> 00:04:00,290
Sir, do you want a position in the government ?

40
00:04:00,980 --> 00:04:02,730
I’ll talk with him about this.

41
00:04:05,940 --> 00:04:07,530
Before the Emperor left the Palace,

42
00:04:07,780 --> 00:04:09,850
he asked me to repair the Hall of Supreme Harmony.

43
00:04:10,980 --> 00:04:12,090
But before I started,

44
00:04:12,940 --> 00:04:14,850
the Empress, Concubine Shu and he

45
00:04:15,310 --> 00:04:17,170
were driven out of the Palace.

46
00:04:18,579 --> 00:04:23,410
I wrote several letters to those senators and

47
00:04:23,420 --> 00:04:24,290
ministers.

48
00:04:24,980 --> 00:04:25,930
I told them

49
00:04:26,340 --> 00:04:27,690
if it couldn’t be repaired immediately,

50
00:04:28,090 --> 00:04:31,130
the Hall of Supreme Harmony would collapse.

51
00:04:33,260 --> 00:04:34,370
But they

52
00:04:35,900 --> 00:04:37,490
didn’t believe it.

53
00:04:38,260 --> 00:04:38,970
Tomorrow,

54
00:04:39,900 --> 00:04:40,650
no,

55
00:04:41,940 --> 00:04:42,850
tonight,

56
00:04:43,980 --> 00:04:45,970
I’ll talk with my brother-in-law about this.

57
00:04:47,220 --> 00:04:48,850
I’ll pay

58
00:04:50,900 --> 00:04:52,730
for the restoration.

59
00:05:05,900 --> 00:05:07,410
Dasheng, stop.

60
00:05:09,780 --> 00:05:10,650
What’s the matter, leader?

61
00:05:10,660 --> 00:05:12,290
Go through the eastern road.

62
00:05:12,580 --> 00:05:13,930
It’s not convenient to

63
00:05:13,940 --> 00:05:15,290
go through that narrow and dark road.

64
00:05:15,300 --> 00:05:16,890
Spring troupe will finish their show.

65
00:05:16,900 --> 00:05:17,890
Don’t let them laugh at us.

66
00:05:35,900 --> 00:05:36,810
Mr. Shang.

67
00:05:41,380 --> 00:05:42,090
Mr. Cheng.

68
00:05:42,820 --> 00:05:43,610
Mr. Shang.

69
00:05:44,180 --> 00:05:45,610
Where are you going?

70
00:05:46,980 --> 00:05:49,210
I’ll take my troupe back to Pingyang.

71
00:05:49,220 --> 00:05:50,170
Go back to Pingyang?

72
00:05:50,860 --> 00:05:51,530
Why?

73
00:05:52,540 --> 00:05:54,210
Won’t you build a new theatre?

74
00:05:54,220 --> 00:05:55,730
How do we build a new one?

75
00:05:56,060 --> 00:05:57,850
These senior peers

76
00:05:58,340 --> 00:06:00,130
stole the money that we have earned for years.

77
00:06:00,530 --> 00:06:01,650
We have no choice.

78
00:06:01,660 --> 00:06:02,400
Shijiu.

79
00:06:09,900 --> 00:06:10,810
Mr. Cheng.

80
00:06:11,400 --> 00:06:14,010
Peking is the origin of Peking opera.

81
00:06:14,540 --> 00:06:16,050
We go back and perform in Pingyang.

82
00:06:16,260 --> 00:06:17,490
When we save enough money

83
00:06:17,620 --> 00:06:18,730
and this thing is solved,

84
00:06:19,100 --> 00:06:20,330
I’ll come back

85
00:06:20,580 --> 00:06:22,210
to continue my career.

86
00:06:22,620 --> 00:06:23,930
I’ll give you tickets then.

87
00:06:57,980 --> 00:06:58,850
Mr. Shang,

88
00:06:59,780 --> 00:07:00,810
can we talk alone?

89
00:07:15,620 --> 00:07:17,810
I make friends with you sincerely.

90
00:07:18,180 --> 00:07:20,490
But you didn’t tell me

91
00:07:20,520 --> 00:07:21,450
about such an important thing.

92
00:07:21,460 --> 00:07:22,690
And you’re leaving in such a hurry.

93
00:07:23,300 --> 00:07:25,090
Don’t you believe that I can help you?

94
00:07:26,980 --> 00:07:29,490
That you help me is what I’m afraid of.

95
00:07:31,220 --> 00:07:33,930
Our friendship is pure like that in operas.

96
00:07:34,700 --> 00:07:36,490
I don't want it to be involved in other things.

97
00:07:37,180 --> 00:07:39,730
It will be vulgar when it’s related to money.

98
00:07:40,060 --> 00:07:41,409
In operas, people

99
00:07:42,220 --> 00:07:43,810
spend thousands of money to get a soul mate.

100
00:07:44,980 --> 00:07:46,409
Now, my soul mate is in trouble.

101
00:07:46,780 --> 00:07:48,170
How can I ignore this?

102
00:07:49,180 --> 00:07:50,970
I won’t forgive myself.

103
00:07:51,380 --> 00:07:52,250
Mr. Cheng, please don’t say that.

104
00:07:52,260 --> 00:07:53,130
Mr. Shang.

105
00:07:55,340 --> 00:07:56,090
Mr. Cheng.

106
00:07:56,409 --> 00:07:57,590
If you were Fan Juqing,

107
00:07:57,990 --> 00:07:59,290
there must be Zhang Yuanbo.

108
00:08:00,300 --> 00:08:01,530
When you are alone,

109
00:08:02,460 --> 00:08:04,050
the opera won’t be complete.

110
00:08:06,420 --> 00:08:07,610
So you

111
00:08:10,420 --> 00:08:12,010
will be my stage?

112
00:08:13,700 --> 00:08:14,610
Yes.

113
00:08:27,060 --> 00:08:27,530
What?

114
00:08:28,020 --> 00:08:30,090
What are they talking about?

115
00:08:31,340 --> 00:08:32,370
I’m so cold.

116
00:08:36,940 --> 00:08:37,890
The leader comes back.

117
00:08:43,500 --> 00:08:44,169
Everyone!

118
00:08:44,860 --> 00:08:46,690
We don’t leave today!

119
00:08:47,020 --> 00:08:48,810
We don’t leave?

120
00:08:48,900 --> 00:08:50,330
We don’t leave today,

121
00:08:51,260 --> 00:08:52,730
and we won’t leave ever.

122
00:08:53,260 --> 00:08:54,970
We must be successful

123
00:08:55,420 --> 00:08:57,210
in Peking.

124
00:08:58,210 --> 00:08:59,850
Let me introduce him again.

125
00:09:01,100 --> 00:09:03,050
Cheng Fengtai, Mr. Cheng,

126
00:09:03,340 --> 00:09:05,490
the shareholder of our Shuiyun Theater.

127
00:09:13,460 --> 00:09:15,090
I watched your opera.

128
00:09:16,300 --> 00:09:18,570
You are all talented performers.

129
00:09:19,260 --> 00:09:22,410
Pingyang can’t give you a stage to show yourself.

130
00:09:23,140 --> 00:09:24,450
You are driven into a corner

131
00:09:24,940 --> 00:09:26,570
because you offended Commander Cao,

132
00:09:26,860 --> 00:09:28,410
and you are short of money.

133
00:09:29,980 --> 00:09:31,570
I am Commander Cao’s brother-in-law.

134
00:09:32,180 --> 00:09:32,890
I’m not afraid of him

135
00:09:33,460 --> 00:09:34,610
even though others are.

136
00:09:35,820 --> 00:09:36,770
And when it comes to money,

137
00:09:38,580 --> 00:09:40,130
I have no shortage of that.

138
00:09:41,660 --> 00:09:43,730
If you trust me,

139
00:09:44,180 --> 00:09:45,290
I, Cheng Fengtai,

140
00:09:45,820 --> 00:09:49,090
will be the backer of Shuiyun Theater.

141
00:09:50,140 --> 00:09:51,570
I protect your performance,

142
00:09:53,020 --> 00:09:54,970
so please make your stage bright for me.

143
00:09:55,200 --> 00:09:56,410
We don’t need to go!

144
00:09:56,420 --> 00:09:58,170
We’ll have a stage again.

145
00:09:59,060 --> 00:10:00,230
Great!

146
00:10:00,240 --> 00:10:01,830
We’ll have a stage again.

147
00:10:05,240 --> 00:10:07,560
♫ Concubine ♫

148
00:10:08,110 --> 00:10:12,810
♫Wait for me to walk with you later ♫

149
00:10:13,780 --> 00:10:21,410
Bravo! Bravo!

150
00:10:30,100 --> 00:10:30,970
Mr. Tian takes office,

151
00:10:30,980 --> 00:10:33,370
and exposes Minister Tong’s trick,

152
00:10:33,380 --> 00:10:34,970
which draws much attention.

153
00:10:35,180 --> 00:10:36,690
Ministers Tong is discharged from his position.

154
00:10:36,700 --> 00:10:38,410
- Liu Zu’ning sees Mr. Tian...
- Be concentrated!

155
00:10:38,420 --> 00:10:40,450
...as a thorn in his side.

156
00:10:40,460 --> 00:10:42,570
He colludes with the newspaper offices

157
00:10:42,580 --> 00:10:44,850
and spreads the rumor that Mr. Tian

158
00:10:44,860 --> 00:10:46,450
offends the Commander Zhang.

159
00:10:46,460 --> 00:10:48,010
It sounds like a story

160
00:10:48,020 --> 00:10:49,530
of our leader.

161
00:10:49,540 --> 00:10:50,330
Yes.

162
00:10:50,340 --> 00:10:52,210
Mr. Tian is our leader,

163
00:10:53,060 --> 00:10:55,610
and Liu Zuning is Jiang Rongshou.

164
00:10:55,620 --> 00:10:57,010
Who wrote this?

165
00:10:57,220 --> 00:10:57,970
Interesting.

166
00:10:58,460 --> 00:10:58,930
Let me have a look.

167
00:10:58,940 --> 00:10:59,490
Don’t rob it.

168
00:10:59,500 --> 00:11:00,770
Give me back.

169
00:11:06,340 --> 00:11:07,290
What are you doing?

170
00:11:07,660 --> 00:11:08,930
You look furtive.

171
00:11:08,940 --> 00:11:09,890
You must be a thief.

172
00:11:09,900 --> 00:11:10,970
No. No.

173
00:11:10,980 --> 00:11:11,730
Don’t misunderstand.

174
00:11:11,740 --> 00:11:12,610
Don’t misunderstand.

175
00:11:12,900 --> 00:11:13,570
I am a journalist.

176
00:11:13,980 --> 00:11:15,010
A journalist from a newspaper office.

177
00:11:15,020 --> 00:11:16,450
Mr. Qiu?

178
00:11:16,660 --> 00:11:18,330
What brings you by?

179
00:11:18,650 --> 00:11:20,930
I heard that Mr. Shang will leave Peking.

180
00:11:21,340 --> 00:11:22,530
I am his die-hard fan.

181
00:11:22,860 --> 00:11:24,730
So I come to take a picture for memory.

182
00:11:25,260 --> 00:11:27,290
Who told you that we are leaving?

183
00:11:28,660 --> 00:11:29,290
Now

184
00:11:29,300 --> 00:11:31,780
Shuiyun Theater’s attendance rate is the highest in Peking.

185
00:11:31,900 --> 00:11:32,890
Why do we leave?

186
00:11:33,460 --> 00:11:36,210
Isn’t Mr. Shang afraid

187
00:11:36,700 --> 00:11:38,690
that Commander Cao will execute him?

188
00:11:38,700 --> 00:11:39,450
What are you talking about?

189
00:11:39,460 --> 00:11:40,210
What are you talking about?

190
00:11:40,980 --> 00:11:43,490
If Commander Cao wants to execute our leader,

191
00:11:43,930 --> 00:11:46,250
he has to discuss it with his brother-in-law

192
00:11:46,620 --> 00:11:47,690
in case that

193
00:11:47,700 --> 00:11:50,050
what his brother-in-law paid

194
00:11:50,060 --> 00:11:51,630
will be in vain.

195
00:11:52,260 --> 00:11:53,970
What do you mean?

196
00:11:54,860 --> 00:11:56,890
Cheng Fengtai, Mr. Cheng,

197
00:11:56,900 --> 00:11:59,210
is our shareholder now.

198
00:11:59,220 --> 00:12:02,090
He’ll build a theater for us.

199
00:12:02,100 --> 00:12:02,690
Shijiu!

200
00:12:03,740 --> 00:12:04,850
Mind your words.

201
00:12:06,860 --> 00:12:08,130
Cheng Fengtai?

202
00:12:23,700 --> 00:12:24,810
Mr. Jiang.

203
00:12:25,460 --> 00:12:27,250
Come to the point.

204
00:12:27,900 --> 00:12:29,210
What do you want me to do?

205
00:12:30,540 --> 00:12:33,890
I want you to stop Shang Xirui building a theatre.

206
00:12:36,380 --> 00:12:38,300
You are the chairman.

207
00:12:38,540 --> 00:12:40,370
So you must know how to do.

208
00:12:42,940 --> 00:12:44,890
Yes, I do.

209
00:12:45,780 --> 00:12:46,930
But I

210
00:12:47,660 --> 00:12:51,010
like watching Mr. Shang’s performance.

211
00:12:52,540 --> 00:12:54,410
Why do we bring trouble to him?

212
00:12:55,780 --> 00:12:57,570
You must not know

213
00:12:58,620 --> 00:12:59,690
that Shang Xirui

214
00:13:00,300 --> 00:13:03,010
has a backer, Cheng Fengtai.

215
00:13:04,540 --> 00:13:05,770
Cheng Fengtai

216
00:13:05,780 --> 00:13:08,730
bought him the land.

217
00:13:13,500 --> 00:13:14,770
If you stop him,

218
00:13:15,260 --> 00:13:17,010
you’ll help me and also,

219
00:13:17,820 --> 00:13:20,690
this is a warning to Cheng Fengtai

220
00:13:21,700 --> 00:13:23,210
that money is not the license

221
00:13:23,980 --> 00:13:27,370
of everything in Peking.

222
00:13:30,140 --> 00:13:31,210
OK.

223
00:13:32,380 --> 00:13:35,610
I’ll take this bottle.

224
00:13:46,700 --> 00:13:48,250
I lost that lucky place.

225
00:13:49,740 --> 00:13:52,650
I promised to build a theater there
when I have enough money,

226
00:13:52,980 --> 00:13:54,650
but it was sold to another one immediately.

227
00:13:56,180 --> 00:13:57,490
Don’t believe their bragging.

228
00:13:58,540 --> 00:14:00,410
If Bodhi court is really a lucky place,

229
00:14:00,940 --> 00:14:02,490
how come it’s taken by eunuchs?

230
00:14:03,460 --> 00:14:04,490
Don’t worry.

231
00:14:05,100 --> 00:14:06,770
Let’s find a new place.

232
00:14:06,780 --> 00:14:08,170
None is better than there.

233
00:14:08,780 --> 00:14:10,650
Other places are too remote

234
00:14:10,980 --> 00:14:12,490
or too bleak.

235
00:14:12,940 --> 00:14:14,810
Good places are all taken.

236
00:14:14,820 --> 00:14:16,490
Then buy a theater directly.

237
00:14:18,220 --> 00:14:19,530
I’ll ask Fan Lian to do it.

238
00:14:19,540 --> 00:14:20,850
But it costs time.

239
00:14:23,780 --> 00:14:24,650
Don’t be hurried.

240
00:14:24,940 --> 00:14:27,410
I have a theatre to perform anyway.

241
00:14:27,820 --> 00:14:29,090
So don’t hurry to find a new one.

242
00:14:30,980 --> 00:14:31,810
Also,

243
00:14:32,940 --> 00:14:34,130
how will you deal with

244
00:14:34,540 --> 00:14:37,050
those who steal money from your troupe?

245
00:14:38,420 --> 00:14:39,900
You don’t always keep

246
00:14:40,620 --> 00:14:42,250
your eyes on them,

247
00:14:42,500 --> 00:14:43,610
so they have chances to do things stealthily.

248
00:14:45,540 --> 00:14:47,250
They may sell you one day

249
00:14:47,660 --> 00:14:49,930
when you don’t notice.

250
00:14:54,300 --> 00:14:55,770
Mean people

251
00:14:55,780 --> 00:14:57,170
don’t have friends.

252
00:14:57,340 --> 00:14:58,690
It’s always like this.

253
00:14:59,260 --> 00:15:00,380
If you are

254
00:15:00,610 --> 00:15:01,670
like them,

255
00:15:02,060 --> 00:15:03,050
that’s fine.

256
00:15:03,860 --> 00:15:04,970
But you are not.

257
00:15:06,810 --> 00:15:07,770
You focus

258
00:15:08,180 --> 00:15:09,210
on friendship.

259
00:15:09,780 --> 00:15:11,290
You are a good friend,

260
00:15:11,900 --> 00:15:13,730
but you are not a good boss.

261
00:15:13,740 --> 00:15:15,970
Who isn’t a good boss?

262
00:15:16,140 --> 00:15:18,160
Don’t I lead them well on opera?

263
00:15:18,220 --> 00:15:19,890
I don’t mean on opera.

264
00:15:20,660 --> 00:15:22,730
I mean on business.

265
00:15:24,340 --> 00:15:26,170
What does a good management need?

266
00:15:27,660 --> 00:15:28,770
It doesn’t need loyalty

267
00:15:29,290 --> 00:15:30,410
or temper.

268
00:15:31,140 --> 00:15:32,290
It needs disciplines

269
00:15:32,300 --> 00:15:33,370
and rules.

270
00:15:34,220 --> 00:15:35,690
Look at other troupes.

271
00:15:36,180 --> 00:15:37,410
They are all under strict rules.

272
00:15:37,820 --> 00:15:40,090
That’s what a good boss should do.

273
00:15:41,660 --> 00:15:43,610
I can’t learn it well.

274
00:15:43,620 --> 00:15:44,770
My time is

275
00:15:44,780 --> 00:15:46,650
for studying opera.

276
00:15:49,620 --> 00:15:50,730
Yes.

277
00:15:51,460 --> 00:15:55,610
It’s not your style if you

278
00:15:56,420 --> 00:15:58,250
teach them rules strictly.

279
00:15:59,740 --> 00:16:00,410
Forget it.

280
00:16:01,300 --> 00:16:02,090
Let me do it.

281
00:16:03,540 --> 00:16:04,490
I am the shareholder.

282
00:16:04,700 --> 00:16:05,490
So my words

283
00:16:05,740 --> 00:16:06,690
will work for them.

284
00:16:07,420 --> 00:16:09,490
Money talks after all.

285
00:16:12,260 --> 00:16:14,170
Leading a troupe is even harder

286
00:16:15,220 --> 00:16:17,050
than leading a troop.

287
00:16:17,780 --> 00:16:20,810
Artists never obey your rules.

288
00:16:21,380 --> 00:16:22,730
Mr. Cheng, can you make it?

289
00:16:27,020 --> 00:16:28,530
Don’t underestimate me.

290
00:16:30,460 --> 00:16:32,330
Let’s wait and see.

291
00:16:32,740 --> 00:16:33,490
Listen.

292
00:16:33,500 --> 00:16:34,690
Paris in France

293
00:16:34,700 --> 00:16:36,050
is very beautiful.

294
00:16:36,620 --> 00:16:38,490
People are tall and strong.

295
00:16:39,330 --> 00:16:42,050
They have cheek kissing when they meet.

296
00:16:42,680 --> 00:16:44,650
That’s an amazing city.

297
00:16:44,660 --> 00:16:45,530
Do you understand?

298
00:16:46,140 --> 00:16:46,970
Leader.

299
00:16:46,980 --> 00:16:47,850
Finally you are back!

300
00:16:47,880 --> 00:16:48,290
Leader! Leader!

301
00:16:48,300 --> 00:16:49,530
Look who is here.

302
00:16:57,940 --> 00:16:58,810
Rui!

303
00:16:59,500 --> 00:17:00,650
Mr. Du.

304
00:17:01,020 --> 00:17:01,570
Take care.

305
00:17:01,580 --> 00:17:02,410
Rui!

306
00:17:02,420 --> 00:17:03,930
I’m back, Rui!

307
00:17:07,260 --> 00:17:07,930
Superstar,

308
00:17:08,380 --> 00:17:09,410
did you miss me ?

309
00:17:09,540 --> 00:17:10,849
When did you come back?

310
00:17:10,859 --> 00:17:12,050
You ask me?

311
00:17:12,060 --> 00:17:13,609
I wanted to give you a surprise.

312
00:17:13,619 --> 00:17:15,930
So I came to you after I arrived in Peking last night.

313
00:17:15,940 --> 00:17:16,530
But

314
00:17:17,140 --> 00:17:18,010
no one was here.

315
00:17:18,819 --> 00:17:20,369
I heard

316
00:17:20,660 --> 00:17:22,609
that Jiang Rongshou brought you troubles.

317
00:17:22,619 --> 00:17:23,650
He drove you out.

318
00:17:24,060 --> 00:17:25,490
How arrogant he is!

319
00:17:25,819 --> 00:17:26,369
So

320
00:17:26,819 --> 00:17:29,250
I wrote a story a whole night for revenge.

321
00:17:29,580 --> 00:17:30,050
Have a look.

322
00:17:30,300 --> 00:17:31,370
A story about me?

323
00:17:33,320 --> 00:17:34,090
Look at me...

324
00:17:36,660 --> 00:17:37,770
Sorry that I forgot to introduce you.

325
00:17:38,460 --> 00:17:39,410
Mr. Du.

326
00:17:39,420 --> 00:17:42,050
This is the shareholder of Shuiyun Theater,

327
00:17:42,060 --> 00:17:43,730
Cheng Fengtai, Mr. Cheng.

328
00:17:43,740 --> 00:17:44,530
Mr. Cheng,

329
00:17:44,540 --> 00:17:45,090
He

330
00:17:45,100 --> 00:17:47,090
is Du Luocheng

331
00:17:47,380 --> 00:17:48,690
from the Imperial Academy.

332
00:17:48,700 --> 00:17:50,930
He writes librettos for me.

333
00:17:52,900 --> 00:17:53,650
Mr. Du.

334
00:17:54,300 --> 00:17:55,010
Nice to meet you.

335
00:17:55,400 --> 00:17:56,480
Screw you!

336
00:17:57,380 --> 00:17:58,650
What’s wrong?

337
00:17:58,660 --> 00:17:59,330
What happened?

338
00:17:59,340 --> 00:18:00,410
Heartbreaker!

339
00:18:01,140 --> 00:18:02,090
Heartbreaker?

340
00:18:03,340 --> 00:18:04,770
You must make a mistake.

341
00:18:04,780 --> 00:18:06,690
I find you finally!

342
00:18:08,540 --> 00:18:09,250
Mr. Du.

343
00:18:09,260 --> 00:18:10,290
Mr. Du! Mr. Du!

344
00:18:10,300 --> 00:18:11,370
Stop it! Go down!

345
00:18:11,740 --> 00:18:12,370
What?

346
00:18:12,380 --> 00:18:13,170
Mr. Du!

347
00:18:13,540 --> 00:18:14,490
Stop it!

348
00:18:14,820 --> 00:18:16,370
Fight in Shuiyun Theater?

349
00:18:16,380 --> 00:18:17,370
Is this approved by our pioneer?

350
00:18:17,380 --> 00:18:18,210
You pushed me?

351
00:18:18,980 --> 00:18:20,210
I am your God of Literature!

352
00:18:20,220 --> 00:18:21,530
I am his God of Wealth!

353
00:18:21,820 --> 00:18:23,130
How dare you talk back?

354
00:18:24,500 --> 00:18:25,470
Alright. Alright.

355
00:18:25,490 --> 00:18:26,190
Stop fighting.

356
00:18:26,740 --> 00:18:27,850
That’s enough.

357
00:18:27,860 --> 00:18:29,730
You both studied abroad.

358
00:18:30,140 --> 00:18:32,250
How can well-educated people fight?

359
00:18:32,260 --> 00:18:33,050
Also, none of you is good at fighting.

360
00:18:33,060 --> 00:18:33,930
Don’t you feel embarrassed to fight

361
00:18:33,940 --> 00:18:34,890
without any practical skill?

362
00:18:36,380 --> 00:18:37,370
I feel embarrassed?

363
00:18:38,500 --> 00:18:39,690
He abandoned his lover.

364
00:18:39,700 --> 00:18:40,890
It’s he who’s embarrassed!

365
00:18:40,900 --> 00:18:42,010
I must teach you a lesson today!

366
00:18:43,740 --> 00:18:44,690
Stop! Stop!

367
00:18:45,780 --> 00:18:47,050
It’s weird.

368
00:18:47,060 --> 00:18:48,170
Who is heartbroken for me?

369
00:18:49,140 --> 00:18:49,890
Stop it!

370
00:18:50,700 --> 00:18:51,330
-No...
-Stop!

371
00:18:51,340 --> 00:18:51,730
Mr. Du.

372
00:18:51,740 --> 00:18:52,690
Tell us

373
00:18:52,700 --> 00:18:54,010
how he makes you heartbroken?

374
00:18:54,340 --> 00:18:54,850
Yes.

375
00:18:54,860 --> 00:18:55,530
Yeah.

376
00:18:55,540 --> 00:18:56,530
Not me.

377
00:18:58,580 --> 00:18:59,370
Cheng Fengtai,

378
00:18:59,820 --> 00:19:00,890
listen carefully!

379
00:19:01,060 --> 00:19:02,010
Su Shanna.

380
00:19:02,500 --> 00:19:03,090
Who?

381
00:19:03,580 --> 00:19:04,770
Su Shanna.

382
00:19:05,340 --> 00:19:06,770
Who?

383
00:19:06,850 --> 00:19:07,900
Su Shanna.

384
00:19:10,220 --> 00:19:11,650
You mean her?

385
00:19:11,660 --> 00:19:12,490
Her?

386
00:19:12,860 --> 00:19:13,850
You think of her?

387
00:19:14,940 --> 00:19:16,210
Don’t deny it.

388
00:19:16,780 --> 00:19:21,490
Su Shanna loved you so much.

389
00:19:21,500 --> 00:19:22,410
Go away!

390
00:19:24,180 --> 00:19:26,210
She loved him so much.

391
00:19:26,860 --> 00:19:29,170
She said that she would only marry him.

392
00:19:29,780 --> 00:19:31,970
She also took his photo with her

393
00:19:31,980 --> 00:19:32,850
and looked at it every day.

394
00:19:32,860 --> 00:19:34,250
She was almost crazy.

395
00:19:34,980 --> 00:19:35,850
But he?

396
00:19:36,740 --> 00:19:38,450
He went back without telling Su Shanna.

397
00:19:41,660 --> 00:19:43,530
Cheng Fengtai.

398
00:19:43,940 --> 00:19:44,730
Tell me,

399
00:19:45,660 --> 00:19:47,250
are you wronged

400
00:19:48,020 --> 00:19:49,010
to be called “heartbreaker”?

401
00:19:51,580 --> 00:19:53,290
If you must say so,

402
00:19:53,980 --> 00:19:55,930
I’m really wronged.

403
00:19:55,940 --> 00:19:57,370
Are you provoking?

404
00:19:58,180 --> 00:19:58,890
How dare you?

405
00:19:58,900 --> 00:19:59,250
Mr. Du!

406
00:19:59,260 --> 00:20:00,610
Take it down.

407
00:20:03,980 --> 00:20:06,130
When I studied in Britain,

408
00:20:06,820 --> 00:20:09,410
a girl named Su Shanna was my classmate

409
00:20:10,620 --> 00:20:11,810
and my friend.

410
00:20:12,580 --> 00:20:13,530
Su Shanna

411
00:20:13,540 --> 00:20:14,290
told me

412
00:20:15,060 --> 00:20:18,050
that an Asian student wooed her.

413
00:20:18,580 --> 00:20:21,530
And he climbed up to her window at night

414
00:20:21,540 --> 00:20:23,050
to give her roses.

415
00:20:23,540 --> 00:20:24,690
It was creepy.

416
00:20:25,060 --> 00:20:25,650
So she

417
00:20:26,540 --> 00:20:28,290
asked me to give her my photo,

418
00:20:28,300 --> 00:20:30,590
and let me disguise as her boyfriend

419
00:20:30,860 --> 00:20:33,500
-to make that boy give up.
-I see.

420
00:20:34,100 --> 00:20:36,170
But it surprised me that

421
00:20:36,860 --> 00:20:40,210
the Asian boy was Mr. Du.

422
00:20:44,820 --> 00:20:46,650
Gosh.

423
00:20:47,020 --> 00:20:48,250
You did so?

424
00:20:48,580 --> 00:20:49,330
Mr. Du.

425
00:20:49,940 --> 00:20:51,410
Look at your thin limbs.

426
00:20:51,860 --> 00:20:53,250
How could you climb up to her window?

427
00:20:57,380 --> 00:21:00,930
Do you know Romeo and Juliet?

428
00:21:02,130 --> 00:21:03,290
No.

429
00:21:03,420 --> 00:21:04,610
It’s because of love.

430
00:21:07,180 --> 00:21:08,010
Love.

431
00:21:09,620 --> 00:21:10,450
Mr. Du.

432
00:21:11,020 --> 00:21:12,650
If you climbs up to my window,

433
00:21:13,020 --> 00:21:15,370
I’ll say yes to you.

434
00:21:15,860 --> 00:21:17,010
Look at you.

435
00:21:18,220 --> 00:21:19,370
What a pity.

436
00:21:20,420 --> 00:21:23,050
Su Shanna never loved you.

437
00:21:24,020 --> 00:21:24,850
Of course,

438
00:21:25,300 --> 00:21:26,330
she never loved me as well.

439
00:21:26,780 --> 00:21:28,530
She loved Vikings

440
00:21:29,100 --> 00:21:31,730
and thought Asian men are not strong enough.

441
00:21:33,220 --> 00:21:34,010
You don’t believe?

442
00:21:35,180 --> 00:21:36,170
Look.

443
00:21:36,620 --> 00:21:39,690
Why must she play the mermaid

444
00:21:39,700 --> 00:21:40,970
instead of the princess?

445
00:21:41,780 --> 00:21:44,130
Just to be held by that Dane.

446
00:21:49,740 --> 00:21:51,650
I should have exercised my muscles.

447
00:21:55,540 --> 00:21:56,730
Alright. Alright.

448
00:21:57,620 --> 00:21:58,330
Mr. Shang.

449
00:21:58,340 --> 00:21:59,450
I need to go back to pack things up.

450
00:21:59,460 --> 00:22:00,450
Goodbye.

451
00:22:01,340 --> 00:22:02,010
Take care, Mr. Cheng.

452
00:22:02,540 --> 00:22:03,410
Mr. Du.

453
00:22:03,620 --> 00:22:05,170
Let’s chat another day.

454
00:22:05,620 --> 00:22:06,250
By the way.

455
00:22:07,140 --> 00:22:07,890
Next time...

456
00:22:08,660 --> 00:22:09,370
No, this time

457
00:22:09,900 --> 00:22:11,130
when you leave,

458
00:22:11,420 --> 00:22:12,450
go through the gate

459
00:22:12,660 --> 00:22:13,970
instead of the wall.

460
00:22:15,220 --> 00:22:16,090
Bye, Mr. Cheng.

461
00:22:16,660 --> 00:22:17,490
Bye, Mr. Cheng.

462
00:22:17,500 --> 00:22:19,070
-Bye, Mr. Cheng.
-Bye, Mr. Cheng.

463
00:22:28,980 --> 00:22:29,610
Mr. Cheng.

464
00:22:30,340 --> 00:22:31,850
Come to have dinner tonight.

465
00:22:31,860 --> 00:22:34,830
We’ll have the first shareholder’s meeting.

466
00:22:40,580 --> 00:22:41,410
Rui.

467
00:22:42,260 --> 00:22:44,010
When did you make friends with him?

468
00:22:44,860 --> 00:22:45,810
Be careful.

469
00:22:45,820 --> 00:22:46,450
Businessmen are more cunning

470
00:22:46,460 --> 00:22:47,810
than monkeys if they have tails.

471
00:22:47,820 --> 00:22:48,940
How can you play games with him?

472
00:22:49,140 --> 00:22:50,450
I don’t play games with him.

473
00:22:50,460 --> 00:22:51,450
We’ll do great things.

474
00:22:52,540 --> 00:22:53,610
Do great things?

475
00:22:54,100 --> 00:22:55,610
I brought some goods from France for you.

476
00:22:55,620 --> 00:22:56,690
Come. Western goodies.

477
00:22:56,700 --> 00:22:58,050
Did you have chocolates?

478
00:22:58,580 --> 00:23:00,010
So sweet. Trust me.

479
00:23:02,300 --> 00:23:03,370
Finally, we overcame

480
00:23:03,780 --> 00:23:04,890
all the barriers.

481
00:23:05,460 --> 00:23:07,370
We couldn’t stay in Peking

482
00:23:07,380 --> 00:23:09,170
without Mr. Cheng’s help.

483
00:23:09,660 --> 00:23:11,650
Now, toast Mr. Cheng.

484
00:23:16,620 --> 00:23:17,730
I said it before.

485
00:23:18,740 --> 00:23:20,050
I am your backer,

486
00:23:20,660 --> 00:23:22,610
and you make your stage bright for me.

487
00:23:23,220 --> 00:23:24,170
Everyone,

488
00:23:24,740 --> 00:23:26,730
this is our promise.

489
00:23:26,860 --> 00:23:27,730
Toast Mr. Cheng!

490
00:23:28,020 --> 00:23:29,530
Toast Mr. Cheng!

491
00:23:34,460 --> 00:23:35,170
Mr. Cheng.

492
00:23:35,180 --> 00:23:35,890
Enjoy.

493
00:23:35,900 --> 00:23:36,730
Help yourself.

494
00:23:40,140 --> 00:23:40,970
Taste this.

495
00:23:41,820 --> 00:23:42,810
Mr. Cheng. Taste this.

496
00:23:43,020 --> 00:23:43,770
Thanks.

497
00:23:46,320 --> 00:23:46,810
Give me one.

498
00:23:46,820 --> 00:23:47,950
Come.

499
00:23:48,660 --> 00:23:49,620
Eat.

500
00:23:57,950 --> 00:23:58,500
Don’t be hurried.

501
00:24:01,660 --> 00:24:02,890
Contract.

502
00:24:05,540 --> 00:24:07,770
Contract.

503
00:24:11,300 --> 00:24:12,330
One more thing.

504
00:24:13,060 --> 00:24:15,730
Now that Mr. Cheng is our shareholder,

505
00:24:16,180 --> 00:24:18,850
he’ll take care of our finance.

506
00:24:19,620 --> 00:24:21,230
Behave yourselves in the future.

507
00:24:22,100 --> 00:24:23,930
You won’t have room for stealing.

508
00:24:24,740 --> 00:24:26,050
Don’t be nervous.

509
00:24:26,620 --> 00:24:27,770
From now on,

510
00:24:28,380 --> 00:24:31,090
we do things based on the contract.

511
00:24:31,460 --> 00:24:31,930
Contract?

512
00:24:31,940 --> 00:24:33,410
What’s the contract, Mr. Cheng?

513
00:24:34,040 --> 00:24:35,260
-What’s that?
-What is it?

514
00:24:35,340 --> 00:24:36,320
What’s the contract?

515
00:24:47,500 --> 00:24:49,460
(Contract)

516
00:24:50,980 --> 00:24:54,330
This is the new rule of Shuiyun Theatre.

517
00:25:02,340 --> 00:25:05,730
This is the new rule of Shuiyun Theatre.

518
00:25:06,200 --> 00:25:07,690
Everyone should sign your name on it.

519
00:25:08,660 --> 00:25:10,010
Once you sign your name,

520
00:25:10,300 --> 00:25:12,570
you’ll be arrested or accused

521
00:25:13,140 --> 00:25:15,690
if you break the rules.

522
00:25:16,540 --> 00:25:17,570
Be accused?

523
00:25:18,060 --> 00:25:19,090
Such serious?

524
00:25:19,220 --> 00:25:20,530
Is... Is this a contract?

525
00:25:21,420 --> 00:25:22,650
It’s still an indenture to sell ourselves.

526
00:25:22,660 --> 00:25:23,410
Nonsense.

527
00:25:24,420 --> 00:25:26,210
The indenture is valid for your life.

528
00:25:26,500 --> 00:25:28,770
But the validity of this contract is five years.

529
00:25:28,930 --> 00:25:30,170
Five years later,

530
00:25:30,510 --> 00:25:34,090
no one forces you to stay.

531
00:25:35,580 --> 00:25:36,330
Leader.

532
00:25:36,340 --> 00:25:38,050
What if we leave within the five years?

533
00:25:38,060 --> 00:25:40,370
You can go

534
00:25:40,820 --> 00:25:42,450
as long as you pay the liquidated damages.

535
00:25:43,180 --> 00:25:45,610
It’s much less

536
00:25:45,620 --> 00:25:48,250
than that for your previous indenture.

537
00:25:49,100 --> 00:25:50,330
It’s not a long time.

538
00:25:51,460 --> 00:25:52,290
Not bad.

539
00:25:53,860 --> 00:25:54,850
Xiaolai, give me one

540
00:25:54,860 --> 00:25:55,330
in case I’ll forget later.

541
00:25:55,340 --> 00:25:55,890
Give me one.

542
00:25:56,820 --> 00:25:57,770
Everyone has one.

543
00:25:57,780 --> 00:25:58,410
Give me.

544
00:25:58,540 --> 00:25:59,690
Give me. Give me.

545
00:25:59,960 --> 00:26:00,850
Here.

546
00:26:00,860 --> 00:26:02,170
Everyone has one.

547
00:26:02,180 --> 00:26:02,730
One by one.

548
00:26:03,020 --> 00:26:03,570
One by one.

549
00:26:03,580 --> 00:26:04,290
Everyone has one.

550
00:26:04,420 --> 00:26:05,130
Everyone has one.

551
00:26:05,490 --> 00:26:06,560
Here.

552
00:26:08,180 --> 00:26:09,490
It’s only five years.

553
00:26:09,500 --> 00:26:10,610
Time flies by.

554
00:26:10,620 --> 00:26:11,290
Yes.

555
00:26:11,860 --> 00:26:12,730
Where should I sign?

556
00:26:15,340 --> 00:26:16,580
Everyone who was there

557
00:26:16,860 --> 00:26:17,740
signed it.

558
00:26:20,660 --> 00:26:21,790
This is nice.

559
00:26:23,060 --> 00:26:25,050
Anyone can go when they want.

560
00:26:25,060 --> 00:26:26,250
They don’t think I’m a good boss,

561
00:26:26,260 --> 00:26:27,690
and I don’t think they are good staff.

562
00:26:31,300 --> 00:26:33,010
We just had dinner.

563
00:26:33,380 --> 00:26:34,290
Have extra meal?

564
00:26:34,540 --> 00:26:36,290
I’m not full without wheaten food.

565
00:26:36,900 --> 00:26:37,610
Mr. Cheng.

566
00:26:37,620 --> 00:26:38,570
How’s going with the account?

567
00:26:40,620 --> 00:26:41,770
This gives me a headache.

568
00:26:43,380 --> 00:26:45,210
Your account

569
00:26:45,220 --> 00:26:47,130
is more messy than your backstage.

570
00:26:48,540 --> 00:26:50,090
Who took care of the account for you?

571
00:26:54,700 --> 00:26:55,570
No one.

572
00:26:56,260 --> 00:26:57,170
When they needed money,

573
00:26:57,620 --> 00:26:58,930
they drew a line on it.

574
00:27:04,540 --> 00:27:06,450
Mr. Shang.

575
00:27:07,700 --> 00:27:09,690
Your money would never be enough

576
00:27:10,260 --> 00:27:12,050
even if you had a gold mountain.

577
00:27:13,260 --> 00:27:15,650
Many things are not matched

578
00:27:15,660 --> 00:27:17,370
on this account book.

579
00:27:17,810 --> 00:27:18,490
What’s more,

580
00:27:18,780 --> 00:27:20,840
they always used money on what we can’t see.

581
00:27:21,240 --> 00:27:22,620
You won’t know how much you lost.

582
00:27:29,540 --> 00:27:31,370
My mind is as messy as the account.

583
00:27:32,980 --> 00:27:34,370
It’s time to stop.

584
00:27:35,780 --> 00:27:37,060
Mr. Cheng. Have you regretted?

585
00:27:40,140 --> 00:27:41,610
What are you talking about?

586
00:27:42,060 --> 00:27:42,770
I said

587
00:27:42,940 --> 00:27:44,930
“have you regretted”?

588
00:27:47,220 --> 00:27:48,170
Crazy guy.

589
00:27:48,580 --> 00:27:49,610
Give me the shoes.

590
00:27:50,860 --> 00:27:51,450
No.

591
00:27:52,460 --> 00:27:54,130
Once you step on my boat,

592
00:27:54,140 --> 00:27:55,850
don’t try to leave me alone.

593
00:27:58,940 --> 00:28:00,330
I shouldn’t have stepped on your boat.

594
00:28:00,340 --> 00:28:01,500
That’s nonsense.

595
00:28:02,140 --> 00:28:03,090
You entered my room

596
00:28:03,100 --> 00:28:03,770
and had my food,

597
00:28:03,780 --> 00:28:04,690
so you must stay.

598
00:28:06,740 --> 00:28:08,050
This is a troupe,

599
00:28:08,660 --> 00:28:10,050
not a bandits' lair.

600
00:28:10,460 --> 00:28:12,050
Are you kidnapping me?

601
00:28:12,060 --> 00:28:13,410
So what?

602
00:28:19,960 --> 00:28:20,780
OK. OK.

603
00:28:21,910 --> 00:28:22,550
Mr. Shang.

604
00:28:23,380 --> 00:28:24,530
It was just a joke.

605
00:28:25,420 --> 00:28:27,490
Let me smoke outside.

606
00:28:28,460 --> 00:28:29,730
Will you manage my account?

607
00:28:38,640 --> 00:28:39,650
Yes!

608
00:28:40,150 --> 00:28:41,830
Yes! Yes!

609
00:28:43,020 --> 00:28:44,810
I stepped on your boat.

610
00:28:45,900 --> 00:28:48,330
How can I step down?

611
00:28:56,060 --> 00:28:56,840
Give me a ticket.

612
00:28:56,850 --> 00:28:57,630
Can I have a box now?

613
00:28:57,660 --> 00:28:58,290
Hurry.

614
00:29:00,050 --> 00:29:00,640
Don’t crowd.

615
00:29:00,660 --> 00:29:02,120
Don’t crowd. Queue up!

616
00:29:05,700 --> 00:29:06,250
Everyone.

617
00:29:07,420 --> 00:29:08,410
Can you see that?

618
00:29:08,980 --> 00:29:11,090
They all come for us.

619
00:29:12,340 --> 00:29:13,850
Our Spring Theater’s golden days

620
00:29:14,500 --> 00:29:15,770
will come.

621
00:29:16,780 --> 00:29:17,450
Let’s go.

622
00:29:18,620 --> 00:29:19,490
Give me one!

623
00:29:19,500 --> 00:29:21,610
One by one. Don’t crowd!

624
00:29:24,340 --> 00:29:25,320
Why do they come?

625
00:29:27,750 --> 00:29:29,090
Aren’t you from Shuiyun Theater?

626
00:29:31,840 --> 00:29:32,730
Who are you?

627
00:29:33,540 --> 00:29:34,930
The backstage is only for staff.

628
00:29:35,540 --> 00:29:37,010
Didn’t your master teach you?

629
00:29:39,700 --> 00:29:41,410
We Spring Theater will perform tonight.

630
00:29:42,700 --> 00:29:43,970
What are you doing here?

631
00:29:44,460 --> 00:29:45,530
Go. Go.

632
00:29:45,540 --> 00:29:46,690
Ask the manager.

633
00:29:46,700 --> 00:29:47,690
Why should I answer you?

634
00:29:56,340 --> 00:29:57,210
Manager!

635
00:30:00,300 --> 00:30:01,290
Leader.

636
00:30:08,140 --> 00:30:09,250
Manager!

637
00:30:10,100 --> 00:30:10,970
Yes, Mr. Jiang.

638
00:30:11,300 --> 00:30:12,290
I’m sorry, Mr. Jiang.

639
00:30:12,300 --> 00:30:14,940
My staff will go to inform you.

640
00:30:15,740 --> 00:30:16,810
Inform me what?

641
00:30:17,540 --> 00:30:18,290
Well,

642
00:30:18,580 --> 00:30:19,490
from now on,

643
00:30:19,900 --> 00:30:21,240
Shuiyun Theater will perform here

644
00:30:21,250 --> 00:30:22,490
at night.

645
00:30:23,300 --> 00:30:24,290
How about us?

646
00:30:24,300 --> 00:30:25,380
How about us?

647
00:30:33,260 --> 00:30:34,810
How about our Spring Theater?

648
00:30:34,820 --> 00:30:36,690
I’m sorry but you have to perform in the morning.

649
00:30:37,200 --> 00:30:38,650
If you want,

650
00:30:38,660 --> 00:30:40,090
you can perform on Monday.

651
00:30:40,180 --> 00:30:41,010
Why?

652
00:30:41,020 --> 00:30:41,610
Why?

653
00:30:42,500 --> 00:30:44,370
You promised me.

654
00:30:45,380 --> 00:30:46,770
But why you broke your words?

655
00:30:49,340 --> 00:30:51,290
How dare you ignore Chairman Jiang?

656
00:30:52,220 --> 00:30:52,650
Well...

657
00:30:52,660 --> 00:30:53,570
The chairman

658
00:30:53,580 --> 00:30:55,130
can’t fill the auditoriums.

659
00:30:55,620 --> 00:30:59,300
Money is the motivation of business.

660
00:31:02,690 --> 00:31:04,290
Putting me in dilemma?

661
00:31:09,820 --> 00:31:11,050
Remember this.

662
00:31:12,300 --> 00:31:14,370
Wait me.

663
00:31:14,660 --> 00:31:16,330
I’ll tell my dad.

664
00:31:17,260 --> 00:31:19,570
None of you can get away from it.

665
00:31:22,300 --> 00:31:23,210
Shang Xirui.

666
00:31:25,180 --> 00:31:26,930
I’ll see you cry soon.

667
00:31:27,500 --> 00:31:28,010
Go.

668
00:31:35,820 --> 00:31:36,610
Go back!

669
00:31:36,620 --> 00:31:37,490
Yes.

670
00:31:37,500 --> 00:31:38,570
-Are you waiting for our show?
-Go back!

671
00:31:38,900 --> 00:31:40,250
-Go back!
-Go back!

672
00:31:40,260 --> 00:31:41,640
-Go back for your dad.
-What are you waiting for?

673
00:31:41,810 --> 00:31:44,410
Will you watch our performance?

674
00:31:44,420 --> 00:31:46,210
-Catch up with them.
-Go back to your dad.

675
00:31:46,220 --> 00:31:47,710
-Go.
-Go back.

676
00:31:47,820 --> 00:31:49,570
Hurry to go.

677
00:31:50,340 --> 00:31:51,290
What are you looking at?

678
00:31:59,700 --> 00:32:00,730
Leader.

679
00:32:01,820 --> 00:32:04,370
We just drove Spring Theater away.

680
00:32:04,900 --> 00:32:07,810
Jiang Dengbao will incite his dad

681
00:32:07,820 --> 00:32:09,610
to frame you.

682
00:32:10,780 --> 00:32:11,490
They’ve

683
00:32:11,500 --> 00:32:13,060
been hating me for long.

684
00:32:13,740 --> 00:32:14,810
This is not a big deal.

685
00:32:20,620 --> 00:32:21,410
How can you laugh?

686
00:32:22,460 --> 00:32:22,650
(Yahong Theater)

687
00:32:22,650 --> 00:32:26,780
♫ Ices rise ♫
(Yahong Theater)

688
00:32:26,780 --> 00:32:32,930
♫ Ices rise ♫

689
00:32:39,890 --> 00:32:54,100
♫ From the island ♫

690
00:32:54,100 --> 00:32:54,650
Nice!
♫ From the island ♫

691
00:32:54,660 --> 00:32:55,050
Good voice!

692
00:32:55,050 --> 00:32:55,850
♫ Jade Rabbit appears ♫
Good voice!

693
00:32:55,850 --> 00:33:05,500
♫ Jade Rabbit appears ♫

694
00:33:05,500 --> 00:33:06,050
Bravo!
♫ Jade Rabbit appears ♫

695
00:33:11,140 --> 00:33:12,130
Morning, Mr. Cheng.

696
00:33:13,140 --> 00:33:14,170
What happened?

697
00:33:14,860 --> 00:33:15,970
You asked me here in the morning.

698
00:33:16,300 --> 00:33:18,010
What new goods will you show me?

699
00:33:18,260 --> 00:33:18,970
Come in.

700
00:33:19,180 --> 00:33:19,970
Close the door.

701
00:33:22,580 --> 00:33:24,170
I ask you here for something serious.

702
00:33:25,460 --> 00:33:26,490
No.

703
00:33:26,820 --> 00:33:28,010
I’m nervous to death

704
00:33:28,020 --> 00:33:29,170
for your serious thing.

705
00:33:30,180 --> 00:33:31,970
I would like to listen

706
00:33:32,460 --> 00:33:34,570
to the story about beauties, gambling

707
00:33:34,900 --> 00:33:35,970
or opera.

708
00:33:36,980 --> 00:33:39,410
Here is a story about opera.

709
00:33:41,220 --> 00:33:42,890
I’ve made a deal with Shang Xirui.

710
00:33:43,220 --> 00:33:44,130
I’ll bought a theater for him

711
00:33:44,140 --> 00:33:45,250
and invest for Shuiyun Theater.

712
00:33:47,500 --> 00:33:48,970
Is my hearing okay?

713
00:33:51,180 --> 00:33:53,010
You are in league with Shang Xirui?

714
00:33:54,180 --> 00:33:55,330
What do you mean “in league with”?

715
00:33:56,260 --> 00:33:57,130
We hit it off

716
00:33:57,140 --> 00:33:58,170
and appreciate each other.

717
00:33:58,180 --> 00:33:59,050
Do you understand?

718
00:33:59,380 --> 00:33:59,970
Yes.

719
00:34:00,140 --> 00:34:00,810
I understand.

720
00:34:02,330 --> 00:34:04,090
But a theatre costs a fortune.

721
00:34:04,860 --> 00:34:05,930
Dose my sister know it?

722
00:34:05,940 --> 00:34:07,410
I asked you out

723
00:34:08,020 --> 00:34:09,330
to avoid your sister.

724
00:34:10,020 --> 00:34:11,489
You know, she dislikes

725
00:34:11,500 --> 00:34:13,130
those entertainers most.

726
00:34:14,020 --> 00:34:15,489
I won’t succeed

727
00:34:15,780 --> 00:34:16,929
if she knows.

728
00:34:17,739 --> 00:34:19,330
So keep this secret for me.

729
00:34:19,699 --> 00:34:20,570
Don’t speak a word out.

730
00:34:23,060 --> 00:34:24,050
I want you

731
00:34:24,699 --> 00:34:25,489
to be

732
00:34:25,500 --> 00:34:27,130
the manager of the theater.

733
00:34:28,179 --> 00:34:31,290
You always behave like a social butterfly.

734
00:34:31,300 --> 00:34:32,290
You are a suitable person

735
00:34:33,020 --> 00:34:34,650
to receive the guests.

736
00:34:51,980 --> 00:34:52,810
Fengtai.

737
00:34:53,179 --> 00:34:55,449
As the manager,

738
00:34:55,460 --> 00:34:56,650
I won’t get enough profits.

739
00:34:57,960 --> 00:34:58,930
How about this?

740
00:34:59,820 --> 00:35:01,530
I have money now.

741
00:35:01,820 --> 00:35:03,210
Let me buy some shares.

742
00:35:03,220 --> 00:35:04,770
Both of us are shareholders.

743
00:35:05,220 --> 00:35:06,330
Don’t let my sister know.

744
00:35:06,340 --> 00:35:08,260
You are always on a tight budget.

745
00:35:08,740 --> 00:35:10,410
Don’t make a fool of yourself.

746
00:35:10,780 --> 00:35:11,490
Fengtai,

747
00:35:11,940 --> 00:35:12,850
I will buy a share

748
00:35:12,860 --> 00:35:14,290
even if I only have a penny.

749
00:35:15,100 --> 00:35:16,810
Only in this way,

750
00:35:16,820 --> 00:35:18,050
can I be the boss and have my business.

751
00:35:19,740 --> 00:35:20,610
Now

752
00:35:20,620 --> 00:35:22,130
Shang Xirui earns

753
00:35:22,140 --> 00:35:23,850
more than a cinema.

754
00:35:24,740 --> 00:35:26,490
He’s really your cash cow.

755
00:35:27,780 --> 00:35:28,890
Please let me join you.

756
00:35:33,820 --> 00:35:34,770
Fengtai.

757
00:35:43,340 --> 00:35:44,360
Fine.

758
00:35:44,940 --> 00:35:46,210
Buy the shares

759
00:35:46,700 --> 00:35:48,320
as many as you can.

760
00:35:49,100 --> 00:35:52,250
This will be our own business.

761
00:35:52,510 --> 00:35:54,080
If you are still careless,

762
00:35:54,420 --> 00:35:56,730
you are really a loser.

763
00:35:57,420 --> 00:35:58,170
OK.

764
00:35:58,180 --> 00:35:59,330
My God of Wealth.

765
00:35:59,860 --> 00:36:00,810
I’ll strut my stuff.

766
00:36:07,620 --> 00:36:08,770
This is a good thing.

767
00:36:08,780 --> 00:36:09,370
Yes.

768
00:36:10,620 --> 00:36:12,090
How did you think of it?

769
00:36:14,540 --> 00:36:16,650
I’m spying Cheng Fengtai these days.

770
00:36:16,660 --> 00:36:17,610
He avoids as possible as he can

771
00:36:17,620 --> 00:36:18,810
and never responds directly.

772
00:36:24,140 --> 00:36:27,130
Seems that he’ll play dumb with us.

773
00:36:27,940 --> 00:36:29,130
So,

774
00:36:29,140 --> 00:36:30,690
let’s take action as what we planned.

775
00:36:31,380 --> 00:36:31,890
Yes, sir.

776
00:36:33,140 --> 00:36:34,090
Before you go,

777
00:36:34,100 --> 00:36:35,570
remove the bullets in the gun.

778
00:36:36,020 --> 00:36:36,690
Remember,

779
00:36:38,300 --> 00:36:39,450
don’t kill him.

780
00:36:39,940 --> 00:36:40,490
Got it.

781
00:36:41,820 --> 00:36:44,650
He’s a relative of Commander Cao after all.

782
00:36:50,020 --> 00:36:52,610
Bullets can only be used on the battlefield.

783
00:36:53,020 --> 00:36:55,530
Others don’t deserve dying in this way.

784
00:36:56,460 --> 00:36:57,210
Yes.

785
00:37:10,670 --> 00:37:11,450
Hello?

786
00:37:12,420 --> 00:37:13,130
OK.

787
00:37:13,540 --> 00:37:14,330
Mrs. Cheng.

788
00:37:14,580 --> 00:37:16,930
Mr. Ma from the freight agent calls Mr. Cheng.

789
00:37:17,490 --> 00:37:18,750
Tell him Mr. Cheng is not at home.

790
00:37:19,820 --> 00:37:20,890
Sorry, Mr. Cheng is not at home.

791
00:37:22,500 --> 00:37:24,010
He said the thing is urgent.

792
00:37:24,020 --> 00:37:24,930
Only Mr. Cheng can deal with it.

793
00:37:32,060 --> 00:37:32,610
It’s me.

794
00:37:32,820 --> 00:37:33,490
What’s the matter?

795
00:37:33,700 --> 00:37:34,860
It’s the same to tell me.

796
00:37:44,430 --> 00:37:45,010
Mr. Han.

797
00:37:46,180 --> 00:37:46,890
Mrs. Cheng.

798
00:37:46,900 --> 00:37:47,770
Something serious.

799
00:37:48,020 --> 00:37:49,370
Cao Guixiu’s men

800
00:37:49,380 --> 00:37:50,530
detained Mr. Cheng’s goods at the train station.

801
00:37:50,740 --> 00:37:51,890
Childe Cao?

802
00:37:53,340 --> 00:37:56,010
I didn’t know that they have a conflict.

803
00:37:56,460 --> 00:37:57,810
This happened out of the blue.

804
00:37:59,100 --> 00:38:01,170
Find Mr. Cheng back.

805
00:38:01,180 --> 00:38:01,610
OK.

806
00:38:01,620 --> 00:38:02,410
Mrs. Cheng.

807
00:38:03,940 --> 00:38:05,140
Is Mrs. Cao at home?

808
00:38:05,490 --> 00:38:07,230
She went to play mahjong.

809
00:38:08,100 --> 00:38:08,970
Call her back.

810
00:38:09,260 --> 00:38:09,570
OK.

811
00:38:09,580 --> 00:38:10,010
Hurry up.

812
00:38:22,140 --> 00:38:22,810
Mr. Cheng.

813
00:38:23,140 --> 00:38:24,370
Please wait at the box.

814
00:38:24,380 --> 00:38:25,650
Our leader just finished a pork leg.

815
00:38:25,660 --> 00:38:26,750
He’s practicing the opera inside.

816
00:38:27,010 --> 00:38:28,170
So he won’t see anyone.

817
00:38:30,020 --> 00:38:31,210
Including me?

818
00:38:32,340 --> 00:38:33,250
You are our God of Wealth.

819
00:38:33,470 --> 00:38:34,170
You are not included.

820
00:40:07,170 --> 00:40:08,010
What happened?

821
00:40:08,620 --> 00:40:10,650
Why did you call me back in a hurry?

822
00:40:11,580 --> 00:40:12,380
Sis.

823
00:40:13,460 --> 00:40:16,090
Is everything well with Childe Cao?

824
00:40:19,380 --> 00:40:20,730
Why did you ask about him?

825
00:40:22,710 --> 00:40:24,630
Does a girl of Fan family

826
00:40:24,650 --> 00:40:25,780
want to marry him?

827
00:40:27,500 --> 00:40:29,810
Mr. Cheng always told me that he is capable

828
00:40:29,820 --> 00:40:30,690
and generous,

829
00:40:31,300 --> 00:40:33,900
and he will achieve something in the future.

830
00:40:34,220 --> 00:40:36,490
Childe Cao is out of our girls’ league.

831
00:40:37,620 --> 00:40:38,900
Don’t flatter me.

832
00:40:40,180 --> 00:40:41,410
Fengtai only says

833
00:40:41,980 --> 00:40:44,090
that Cao Guixiu is cunning.

834
00:40:44,500 --> 00:40:46,130
He may add something like

835
00:40:46,140 --> 00:40:47,970
“he’s as cunning as my sister”.

836
00:40:47,980 --> 00:40:49,170
Am I right?

837
00:40:49,180 --> 00:40:49,730
No.

838
00:40:50,220 --> 00:40:51,680
You care your family,

839
00:40:52,900 --> 00:40:54,010
but Childe Cao doesn’t.

840
00:40:56,860 --> 00:40:58,340
What did Cao Guixiu do?

841
00:40:59,260 --> 00:41:00,410
He detained some goods of Mr. Cheng

842
00:41:00,420 --> 00:41:01,890
at the train station today.

843
00:41:01,900 --> 00:41:02,730
Sis,

844
00:41:02,740 --> 00:41:04,730
what does he want to do?

845
00:41:07,930 --> 00:41:09,800
Is there a misunderstanding?

846
00:41:09,830 --> 00:41:11,930
Mr. Ma called me at the train station.

847
00:41:11,940 --> 00:41:13,250
So there’s no misunderstanding.

848
00:41:13,260 --> 00:41:13,700
Also...

849
00:41:19,240 --> 00:41:20,500
What?

850
00:41:21,700 --> 00:41:22,770
He said

851
00:41:23,180 --> 00:41:25,410
he must let Mr. Cheng know that he did so.

852
00:41:28,060 --> 00:41:28,900
Sis,

853
00:41:29,340 --> 00:41:31,210
Mr. Cheng works for Commander Cao.

854
00:41:31,220 --> 00:41:33,090
I never ask him about this.

855
00:41:33,420 --> 00:41:35,160
But I know he’s honest

856
00:41:35,460 --> 00:41:36,970
and does everything under rules.

857
00:41:36,980 --> 00:41:38,380
Please don’t get the innocent involved

858
00:41:38,780 --> 00:41:40,370
if Mr. Cao and his son have a conflict.

859
00:41:42,460 --> 00:41:43,250
Rest assured.

860
00:41:44,180 --> 00:41:47,130
I will protect Fengtai.

861
00:41:48,340 --> 00:41:51,290
But he’s not easy to do things between them.

862
00:41:56,860 --> 00:41:57,530
Fengtai.

863
00:42:00,100 --> 00:42:00,970
Have a seat.

864
00:42:01,500 --> 00:42:02,170
Sit.

865
00:42:07,890 --> 00:42:08,370
Sweet heart.

866
00:42:08,380 --> 00:42:08,990
Sit here.

867
00:42:13,240 --> 00:42:13,680
OK.

868
00:42:17,420 --> 00:42:18,650
I can’t see the stage.

869
00:42:42,380 --> 00:42:43,370
I want black tea.

870
